Package edu.rit.crst

Package edu.rit.crst contains the core CryptoStat classes and interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FunctionKernel
    Interface FunctionKernel specifies the interface for a GPU kernel function that evaluates a cryptographic Function on a series of inputs.
    TestKernel
    Interface TestKernel specifies the interface for a GPU kernel function that computes the logarithms of the Bayes factors for all rounds and bit groups for a Test object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Add
    Class Add provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Adjacent
    Class Adjacent provides an object that generates a series of output bit groups for a cryptographic Function.
    Avalanche
    Class Avalanche performs an avalanche Test for a cryptographic Function.
    BitGroup
    Class BitGroup is the abstract base class for an object that generates a series of output bit groups for a cryptographic Function.
    CombiningGenerator
    Class CombiningGenerator is an abstract base class for an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Complement
    Class Complement provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Computation
    Class Computation is the abstract base class for an object that performs a computation on the GPU.
    Concatenate
    Class Concatenate provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Difference
    Class Difference performs a difference Test for a cryptographic Function.
    Direct
    Class Direct performs a direct Test for a cryptographic Function.
    Function
    Class Function is the abstract base class for a cryptographic function.
    Generator
    Class Generator is the abstract base class for an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Gray
    Class Gray provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Interleave
    Class Interleave provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    OneOff
    Class OneOff provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Paste
    Class Paste provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Permute
    Class Permute provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Rand
    Class Rand provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Scattered
    Class Scattered provides an object that generates a series of output bit groups for a cryptographic Function.
    Seq
    Class Seq provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Shift
    Class Shift provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Single
    Class Single provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Test
    Class Test is the abstract base class for an object that performs odds ratio tests for a cryptographic Function.
    TestResult
    Class TestResult provides the Java equivalent of the CUDA testResult_t structure.
    TransformGenerator
    Class TransformGenerator is the abstract base class for an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
    Version
    Class Version contains the CryptoStat version number.
    Xor
    Class Xor provides an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
